!!
!!##DESCRIPTION
!!     islower(3f) returns .true. if character is a miniscule letter (a-z)
!!
!!##OPTIONS
!!    onechar  character to test
!!
!!##RETURNS
!!    islowe  logical value returns true if character is a lowercase
!!             ASCII character else false.
!!##EXAMPLE
!!
